summary: Changes the Winterhold college to make more sense
descriptionHtml:
This does exactly what it says on the tin, the doors on the first floor will now lead to the second floor and the ones on the second floor will lead to the third floor and so on. no longer will the doors on the first floor lead to the third floor etc.

Only downside is that the doors on the sides of the college itself are no longer in use (the ones leading to the balcony). other then that it works like a charm.
author: Lartask
